n\"><a class=\"button primary\" href=\"https://www.neweconomies.co/subscribe?\"><span>Subscribe now</span></a></p><div><hr></div><h4>How podcasters make money &#8212; and why it&#8217;s more powerful than traditional media</h4><p>Creators have something legacy media never had: monetization flexibility.</p><p>Subscriptions<br>Brand deals<br>Ads<br>Affiliates<br>Courses<br>UGC<br>Royalties </p><p>Instead of depending on a single revenue stream, creators can experiment quickly, double down on what works, and drop what doesn&#8217;t. Agility is their superpower.</p><p>Legacy media still leans heavily on ads and subscriptions &#8212; slow, rigid models that limit innovation.</p><p>This is why creators are becoming the new media power players. Their business models simply scale better.</p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.neweconomies.co/p/the-new-titans-of-audio\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!EYC1!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd4a4c7ae-5fb9-445f-ac21-a2b0078cc3ef_9332x5306.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!EYC1!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd4a4c7ae-5fb9-445f-ac21-a2b0078cc3ef_9332x5306.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!EYC1!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd4a4c7ae-5fb9-445f-ac21-a2b0078cc3ef_9332x5306.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!EYC1!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd4a4c7ae-5fb9-445f-ac21-a2b0078cc3ef_9332x5306.png 1456w\" si